---
import ShellWindow from "./ShellWindow.astro";
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import kickoffPoster from "../assets/kickoff-poster-tall.png";
---

<main
	class="w-full px-5 md:px-10 lg:px-20 pb-20 lg:pb-40
		flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 md:gap-10 lg:gap-20
		items-center lg:items-start justify-center
		max-w-7xl"
>
	<section
		class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-10
			font-sans font-medium dark:font-normal
			leading-8 md:leading-10 lg:leading-14
			text-center
			text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl
			text-transparent bg-clip-text
        	bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 dark:from-indigo-500
            from-20% to-fuchsia-800 dark:to-sky-300 to-90%
			z-0 w-full md:w-1/2"
	>
		<h1 class="lg:text-left">
			The command line is a tool of empowerment, and it's for everyone!
		</h1>
		<p
			class="font-light leading-8 lg:leading-10 lg:text-left
			text-xl lg:text-2xl xl:text-3xl max-w-3xl
			text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-400"
		>
			Learn to use your computer's magic portal in a step by step manner,
			no experience required. It will soon be your trusty friend on your
			freedom journey.
		</p>
